            %p.countup The race starts in:
            %p.countdown{:style => "display: none"} It's on! The race has been going for:
            #day
              %b 00
              %span days
            #hrs
              %b 00
              %span hrs
            #min
              %b 00
              %span min
            #sec
              %b 00
              %span sec
          %ul#nav
            %li
              %a{:href => "/home/articles/home"} Home
